		CCG, &lsquo;We&rsquo;, &lsquo;I&rsquo;, mean Capability Charlotte Gardens.
	</p>
	<p>
		&lsquo;The Client&rsquo;, &lsquo;You&rsquo;, mean the person or persons who request CCG to carry out work being liable to pay
