		will cover any fines or damages and indemnify CCG from and against any costs, claims, damages
		liabilities and expenses arising from any breach of planning permission, tree-work or licences in
		respect of the project, if these consents are not obtained. You agree to carry out correct and regular
		horticultural maintenance to facilitate the ongoing establishment of the garden after completion.
	</p>
